data.title: Victoria Memorial High School Classmates Website
data.meta_description: victoriamemorial.houstonclassmates.com is a private alumni website made specifically for current students, alumni and faculty that attended or taught at Victoria Memorial High School, Victoria, TX.  In order to view the website and the members, you must be verified by a current member of the site.

Student Teacher/Faculty

This is a private website intended only for students that attended Victoria Memorial High School in Victoria, TX. Former and current staff members are also permitted to register. All new registrations will have to be verified by either the site administrator or their class administrator.
